<div class='container container--white text-center'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-sm-12'>
      <%= image_tag('bd-tablet.png', class: 'center') %>
      <h1 class='bd--heading'>Install a Bus Detective Display</h1>
      <p class='bd--lead'>
        Suport public transporation in Cincinnati. Display real-time bus arrival data for Cincinnati Metro in your bar, restaurant or retail store.
      </p>
      <%= mail_to 'dschleith@gmail.com', 'Apply Now', subject: 'Bus Detective Partner', class: 'btn btn-default', role: 'button' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='container'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-sm-12'>
      <%= image_tag('bd-photo.jpg', class: 'center full-width') %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='container--white'>
  <div class='container text-center'>
    <div class='row'>
      <div class='col-sm-4'>
        <%= image_tag('bd-attract.svg', class: 'icon') %>
        <div class='bd--list'>
          <h3>Attract Attention</h3>
          <p>Bus Detective displays start conversations and draw people into your business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='col-sm-4'>
        <%= image_tag('bd-sales.svg', class: 'icon') %>
        <div class='bd--list'>
          <h3 class='bd--list-heading'>Increase Sales</h3>
          <p>People stay longer—and buy more—if they know exactly when the bus is coming. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='col-sm-4'>
        <%= image_tag('bd-foot.svg', class: 'icon') %>
        <div class='bd--list'>
          <h3 class='bd--list-heading'>Drive Foot Traffic</h3>
          <p>Encouraging bus ridership creates more foot traffic for your business. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='container--grey text-center'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='row'>
      <div class='col-sm-12'>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Become a Founding Partner with Bus Detective.</p>
        <%= image_tag('bd-founder.svg', class: 'icon--small') %>
      </div>
      <div class='col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3'>
        <div class='well'>
          <p>The first 10 Founding Partner businesses will receive a tablet for $20. We'll install it at your business with the app up and running. It will display routes and arrival times for the nearest bus stops. As a partner, you're responsible for providing WiFi and display space.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3'>
        <p>
          Email
          <%= mail_to 'dschleith@gmail.com', 'Daniel Schleith', subject: 'Bus Detective Partner' %>
          about applying for a display
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='container container--white text-center'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-sm-12'>
      <h2>About This Project </h2>
      <%= image_tag('pl.png', class: 'u-push--ends') %>
    </div>
    <div class='col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3'>
      <p>
        Bus Detective Public Displays are a
        <%= link_to 'People’s Liberty Project Grantee.', 'http://www.peoplesliberty.org/grantees/', target: '_blank' %>
        The team behind the displays includes Daniel Schleith and Nate Wessel, graduate students and public transportation researchers, and Brad Thomas, a SORTA board member.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
